<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 06:09:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于以色列准备应对国际社会对加沙的强烈反对，达成人质协议的可能性似乎很低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/chances-for-a-hostage-deal-seem-low-as-israel-braces-for-international-backlash-over-gaza/0000018e-1a4c-d1cc-abfe-dfedb19b0000</link><description>时任国防部长埃胡德·巴拉克 (Ehud Barak) 曾于 2011 年警告以色列可能遭遇“外交海啸”。当这种情况没有发生时，他的警告遭到了内塔尼亚胡的忠实支持者的嘲笑。但考虑到加沙旷日持久的战争，这就是以色列现在面临的问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/chances-for-a-hostage-deal-seem-low-as-israel-braces-for-international-backlash-over-gaza/0000018e-1a4c-d1cc-abfe-dfedb19b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡是领导人，他应该受到责备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-head-he-is-to-blame/0000018e-1a76-d8fb-abff-5f7e5aae0000</link><description>15 年来，减去 18 个月的中断时间，以色列只有一位总理。近年来，他带领公司从灾难到灾难，从失败到失败，从崩溃到崩溃</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 04:00:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-the-head-he-is-to-blame/0000018e-1a76-d8fb-abff-5f7e5aae0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：谁告诉我们不要在拉法采取行动，谁就告诉我们输掉战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-live/netanyahu-whoever-tells-us-not-to-act-in-rafah-is-telling-us-to-lose-the-war/0000018e-1c1d-d1cc-abfe-dfbd4b750000</link><description>拜登宣布在加沙建立临时港口以运送援助物资 ■ 以色列官员称，以色列欢迎美国修建码头的计划 ■ 美国官员称，人质交易因哈马斯未同意释放病人和老人而被推迟 ■ 以色列外交部称“南非”继续充当哈马斯的合法机构</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 03:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article-live/netanyahu-whoever-tells-us-not-to-act-in-rafah-is-telling-us-to-lose-the-war/0000018e-1c1d-d1cc-abfe-dfbd4b750000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在国情咨文中向以色列发出尖锐信息：不要将加沙援助作为讨价还价的筹码</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/biden-sends-sharp-message-to-israel-during-state-of-the-union-let-aid-into-gaza/0000018e-1bc3-d1cc-abfe-dfef36ee0000</link><description>“人道主义援助不能成为次要考虑因素或讨价还价的筹码。美国总统表示，保护和拯救无辜生命必须成为首要任务</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 03:27:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/biden-sends-sharp-message-to-israel-during-state-of-the-union-let-aid-into-gaza/0000018e-1bc3-d1cc-abfe-dfef36ee0000</guid></item><item><title>只有一个人知道内塔尼亚胡是否偿还了他的百万富翁朋友的贷款 - 但他并没有说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡获得了从斯宾塞·帕特里奇那里贷款的许可，后者此前曾给他买过雪茄和西装。这笔贷款是由总理亲自挑选的国家审计长批准的，该审计长应该通过内塔尼亚胡的资产和利息披露来监督还款，而公众无法获得这些信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-08/ty-article/.premium/only-one-man-knows-if-netanyahu-repaid-loan-from-millionaire-friend-and-hes-not-saying/0000018e-1a5b-d7d3-abce-7afbcd210000</guid></item><item><title>“这是一场残酷的富人之间的战争。以色列在加沙的战斗形式异常浪费”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-war-of-cruel-rich-people-israels-form-of-combat-in-gaza-is-unusually-wasteful/0000018e-1aa8-d1cc-abfe-dfadbc010000</link><description>加沙战争中出现的弹药相关问题将在稍后进行调查。与此同时，他们正在决定军队的战略，并使以色列完全依赖其美国盟友</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 21:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/magazine/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-war-of-cruel-rich-people-israels-form-of-combat-in-gaza-is-unusually-wasteful/0000018e-1aa8-d1cc-abfe-dfadbc010000</guid></item><item><title>正统派政党达成解决拜特谢梅什市长选举决选的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/haredi-parties-cut-deal-to-resolve-run-off-in-beit-shemesh-mayoral-election/0000018e-1a83-d7d3-abce-7aab6cad0000</link><description>Degel Hatorah、Agudat Yisrael 和 Shas 之间的合作协议预计也将对 Bnei Brak 的市政政治和下一次议会选举产生影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 20:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/haredi-parties-cut-deal-to-resolve-run-off-in-beit-shemesh-mayoral-election/0000018e-1a83-d7d3-abce-7aab6cad0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙迫切需要援助。拜登找到解决办法了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-07/ty-article/.highlight/gaza-desperately-needs-aid-is-bidens-new-emergency-port-plan-the-answer/0000018e-19ed-dec4-abcf-dfefa9150000</link><description>由于未能确保停火，紧急港口将成为拜登在国情咨文演讲期间发表的以色列-加沙言论的核心内容。随着斋月的临近，每一分钟的风险都呈指数级增长</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 20:42:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-07/ty-article/.highlight/gaza-desperately-needs-aid-is-bidens-new-emergency-port-plan-the-answer/0000018e-19ed-dec4-abcf-dfefa9150000</guid></item><item><title>以色列获准参加下个月的欧洲歌唱大赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-given-permission-to-participate-in-next-months-eurovision-contest/0000018e-1a3d-d8fb-abff-5f3f935c0000</link><description>经过数周的不确定性和对以色列必须待在家里的真正担忧之后，欧洲广播联盟批准了《飓风》的歌词，该歌词将于周日在 Kan 11 的特别广播中首播</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:06:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-given-permission-to-participate-in-next-months-eurovision-contest/0000018e-1a3d-d8fb-abff-5f3f935c0000</guid></item><item><title>今年妇女节，加沙的巴勒斯坦妇女正在帐篷里制作经期产品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-womens-day-palestinian-women-in-gaza-are-making-period-products-out-of-tents/0000018e-1980-d7d3-abce-79a9bfa90000</link><description>加沙妇女在面临水危机时剪掉头发、在没有麻醉的情况下剖腹产并用废料制作经期产品，在不可能的情况下展现了力量和聪明才智</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 19:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-womens-day-palestinian-women-in-gaza-are-making-period-products-out-of-tents/0000018e-1980-d7d3-abce-79a9bfa90000</guid></item><item><title>OSINT 揭示了自 10 月 7 日以来美国向以色列空运武器的规模空前</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/open-source-intelligence-reveals-the-unprecedented-extent-of-u-s-arms-airlifts-to-israel/0000018e-1976-d021-adef-9f77c76c0000</link><description>据报道，自加沙战争爆发以来，拜登政府已向以色列秘密出售了 100 笔武器。公开的飞行数据显示了它是如何展开的</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/open-source-intelligence-reveals-the-unprecedented-extent-of-u-s-arms-airlifts-to-israel/0000018e-1976-d021-adef-9f77c76c0000</guid></item><item><title>战时的斋月和阿克萨清真寺：加沙战争将如何影响以色列和巴勒斯坦的关键热点？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-timeline/.premium/ramadan-and-al-aqsa-in-wartime-the-gaza-war-and-a-key-israeli-palestinian-flashpoint/0000018e-0ef9-d203-a9ce-1ef989420000</link><description>随着斋月下周开始，本已动荡的中东将面临另一场考验，重点是耶路撒冷的阿克萨清真寺。加沙战争将如何影响以色列和巴勒斯坦的关键热点？ |国土报解释</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article-timeline/.premium/ramadan-and-al-aqsa-in-wartime-the-gaza-war-and-a-key-israeli-palestinian-flashpoint/0000018e-0ef9-d203-a9ce-1ef989420000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 153 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-19e2-dec4-abcf-dfeb7b140000</link><description>拜登宣布美国将在加沙建立临时港口以接收大量援助物资 ■ 哈马斯领导人对停火条款存在分歧 ■ 哈马斯高级官员称以色列“挫败”调解人达成协议的努力 ■ 谈判将至少持续到第一次消息人士称，斋月一周 ■ 以色列国防军开始对导致哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的失误进行内部调查 ■ 战争结束 153 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 18:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-153/0000018e-19e2-dec4-abcf-dfeb7b140000</guid></item><item><title>“我并不爱很多地方，只爱以色列。在德国，即使我不是犹太人，我也会去犹太教堂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/im-not-in-love-with-many-places-only-with-israel/0000018e-19a5-dec4-abcf-dfaf4da00000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：十几岁的克劳斯爱上了一个以色列男孩，最终爱上了以色列。他最近的一次访问是做志愿者并帮助南方的农民</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 16:41:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/im-not-in-love-with-many-places-only-with-israel/0000018e-19a5-dec4-abcf-dfaf4da00000</guid></item><item><title>拜登将宣布在加沙建立紧急港口以便利援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-gaza-war-set-to-feature-in-bidens-state-of-the-union-address/0000018e-1930-d021-adef-9f375a490000</link><description>拜登将在周四晚的国情咨文演讲中宣布，美国军方将领导紧急任务，建立加沙港口以运送援助物资，这可以说是其总统任期内最重要的演讲——17名被哈马斯俘虏或杀害的美国人的亲属在一旁观看</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 16:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-gaza-war-set-to-feature-in-bidens-state-of-the-union-address/0000018e-1930-d021-adef-9f375a490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队开始调查 10 月 7 日之前的故障</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-begins-investigation-of-failures-leading-up-to-october-7/0000018e-1905-d1cc-abfe-dfad95730000</link><description>以色列国防军的调查将审查从 2018 年到 2023 年 10 月 10 日期间，哈马斯致命袭击后重新夺回对加沙边境周边社区的控制</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 14:42:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-begins-investigation-of-failures-leading-up-to-october-7/0000018e-1905-d1cc-abfe-dfad95730000</guid></item><item><title>因意大利政府反对而被撤销西岸市长大使职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-mayors-ambassadorship-revoked-following-italian-govt-opposition/0000018e-18d6-d8fb-abff-5dde377e0000</link><description>意大利政府对任命本尼·卡什里尔（Benny Kasriel）担任以色列驻该国特使表示担忧，因为他住在约旦河西岸。谈判未果，外交部发布了该职位的内部招标</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 13:11:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-mayors-ambassadorship-revoked-following-italian-govt-opposition/0000018e-18d6-d8fb-abff-5dde377e0000</guid></item><item><title>国家检察官阻止对父亲被指控强奸未成年人的以色列 MK 进行审讯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-prevents-interrogation-of-mk-whose-father-is-accused-of-raping-minors/0000018e-184b-d8fb-abff-5d4b7f170000</link><description>MK Yaakov Tessler 涉嫌向一名 15 岁受害者支付封口费，该受害者据称被 Tessler 的父亲强奸。尽管案件已搁置六个月，但他的调查尚未获得国家检察官的授权</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-prevents-interrogation-of-mk-whose-father-is-accused-of-raping-minors/0000018e-184b-d8fb-abff-5d4b7f170000</guid></item><item><title>由于战争，以色列部长取消了一年一度的独立日烟花表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-nixes-annual-independence-day-fireworks-show-due-to-war/0000018e-188a-d1cc-abfe-dfafc31e0000</link><description>利库德集团部长米里·雷格夫对鉴于严峻的形势，第76届独立日仪式未能按照传统举行表示遗憾。两年前，烟花表演也因患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 的退伍军人的反对而被取消</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 11:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-nixes-annual-independence-day-fireworks-show-due-to-war/0000018e-188a-d1cc-abfe-dfafc31e0000</guid></item><item><title>自战争开始以来，已有 27 名加沙被拘留者在以色列军事设施的拘留期间死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/27-gaza-detainees-died-in-custody-at-israeli-army-facilities-since-the-start-of-the-war/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bbaa370000</link><description>返回加沙的被拘留者作证称，他们受到了严酷的待遇，包括士兵和审讯期间的殴打和虐待。以色列国防军发言人表示，军方已对死亡事件展开调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 10:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-07/ty-article/.premium/27-gaza-detainees-died-in-custody-at-israeli-army-facilities-since-the-start-of-the-war/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bbaa370000</guid></item></channel></rss>